    dc:description "Figure 3. (A, B) Linuche sp.: A, Stephanoscyphistoma exoskeleton; B, aboral view. (C–E) Lobonemidae sp. indet.: C, umbrella; D, oral arms; E, umbrellar margin with rhopalium (square). (F, G) Stomolophus sp. 2: F, umbrella; G, oral arms. H, Phacellophora sp.: medusa. Scale bars: A, B=–500 μm. Photographs were taken by Oscar Peña (F) and Javier González (Sociedad Cooperativa Abuloneros y Langostero) (H)." ;
